<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>TSI 94-14-01 - Power Divider Lock (PDL) Control Valve Indicator Light Operation</stitle>
    <tsi id="tsi941401" tsitype="truck">
        <tsinumber>94-14-01</tsinumber>
        <tsidate>May, 1994</tsidate>
        <subjectfile>REAR AXLE</subjectfile>
        <subjectgroup>
            <subject>Power Divider Lock (PDL) Control Valve Indicator Light Operation</subject>
        </subjectgroup>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>This TSI applies to all models with Power Divider.</para>
                <para>The power divider lock engagement indicator light operation has changed with the introduction of
                    the new Power Divider Lock (PDL) control valve.
                </para>
                <para>With the new PDL control valve the indicator light is actuated by the pressure signal being
                    delivered to the power divider lock mechanism. Prior to this change, the power divider lock
                    indicator light was actuated by lever position only. With the new PDL control valve, the light will
                    sometimes be on even with the valve in the "OUT" disengaged position.
                </para>
                <para>Operation of the PDL indicator light with the new PDL control valve is as follows:</para>
                <table id="t9414011" frame="all">
                    <title>PDL Indicator Light Operation</title>
                    <tgroup cols="3" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                        <colspec colwidth="3.76in"/>
                        <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="1.42in"/>
                        <colspec colname="col3" colwidth="1.42in"/>
                        <spanspec namest="col2" nameend="col3" spanname="2to3"/>
                        <thead>
                            <row>
                                <entry valign="top"></entry>
                                <entry colspan="2" spanname="2to3" valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>
                                        <emph type="bold">PDL Control Valve Lever Position</emph>
                                    </para>
                                </entry>
                            </row>
                        </thead>
                        <tbody>
                            <row>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>
                                        <emph type="bold">With 0-35 PSI In Air System</emph>
                                    </para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>
                                        <emph type="bold">In</emph>
                                    </para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>
                                        <emph type="bold">Out</emph>
                                    </para>
                                </entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry valign="top">
                                    <para>Parking brake valve in "Park" position</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>Light On</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>Light On</para>
                                </entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry valign="top">
                                    <para>Parking brake valve in "Release" position</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>Light On</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>Light On</para>
                                </entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>
                                        <emph type="bold">With More Than 35 PSI In Air System</emph>
                                    </para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>
                                        <emph type="bold">In</emph>
                                    </para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>
                                        <emph type="bold">Out</emph>
                                    </para>
                                </entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry valign="top">
                                    <para>Parking brake valve in "Park" position</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>Light On</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>Light On</para>
                                </entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry valign="top">
                                    <para>Parking brake valve in "Release" position</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>Light On</para>
                                </entry>
                                <entry valign="top" align="center">
                                    <para>Light Off</para>
                                </entry>
                            </row>
                        </tbody>
                    </tgroup>
                </table>
                <para>As can be seen from the above table, the only time the indicator light will be off is when the PDL
                    control valve is in the "Out" disengaged position, air pressure is greater than 35 PSI and the
                    parking brakes are released. The light accurately indicates the PDL engagement condition.
                </para>
                <para>The new PDL control valve went into production on Springfield built models on December 1, 1993. It
                    is scheduled to go into production on Chatham built models in June, 1994. The new PDL control valve
                    can be identified by the absence of threads at the air line connection. The new "Fast Connect" air
                    line system is used which doesn't require threads.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
        <partsinfo>
            <para>There are two different new PDL control valves.</para>
            <table id="t9414012" frame="all">
                <title>Parts Information</title>
                <tgroup cols="2" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
